Class CsvAccountBootstrapper

java.lang.Object
data.CsvAccountBootstrapper
public class CsvAccountBootstrapper extends Object
Utility class responsible for bootstrapping (seeding) user accounts from CSV files. This class parses external CSV data and populates the AccountCreationRepository with initial Student, Staff, and Company Representative accounts.
